rem mainframe computer
rem 8/23/2017

do Examine Computer
 [
  print The computer is an old server board design with a top level command display.
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print Though the display is locked out, alarms going off in the building.
   |
    print It sits in the corner, no one operating the terminal.
    setflag examine mainframe
   ]
 ]

ifflag hosaka alarm
 [|
  ifflag examine mainframe
   [
    do Operate Computer
     [
      print Looking at it closer, you see on the display that the system can be cycled into
      print a maintenance mode. Possibly flushing the cryotubes.
      go Computer
     ]
   |]
 ]
